"```sql\nSELECT comments.Text\nFROM comments\nJOIN users ON comments.UserId = users.Id\nWHERE users.DisplayName = 'A Lion';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `Text` of all comments made by the user with the display name \"A Lion.\" It joins the `comments` table with the `users` table using the foreign key relationship `comments.UserId = users.Id` to filter comments by the specified user."